data.meta_description: Jacques Francois Penneman was born on January 30, 1646 in Gand (9000) St Michel Flandre Oriantal Belgique, son of Jacques Penneman and Anne Charlotte Helias. He was married on February  3, 1669 in Gand (9000) St Nicolas Flandre Oriental Belgique to Francoise van Biervliet, they had 2 children. He died on November  2, 1725 in Gand (9000) Flandre Oriantal Belgique. This information is part of Family tree De Pruyssenaere by Jacques van der Meer on Genealogy Online.
